# @description Mandarin Fish UI specialist with RLVR auto-activation

CYAN='\033[0;36m'
GREEN='\033[0;32m'
PURPLE='\033[0;35m'
YELLOW='\033[1;33m'
NC='\033[0m'

echo -e "${PURPLE}üê† MANDARIN FISH UI SPECIALIST${NC}"
echo "=================================================="

# Check RLVR availability
if [ -f "packages/rlvr/package.json" ]; then
    echo -e "${GREEN}‚úÖ RLVR Framework detected${NC}"
    echo -e "${CYAN}üöÄ Auto-activating Mandarin Fish with RLVR...${NC}"
    echo ""
    
    cat << 'EOF'

üê† **MANDARIN FISH RLVR AUTO-ACTIVATED**

You are now operating with RLVR for UI/React development.

MANDATORY INITIALIZATION:
```typescript
import { Agent, getAgentPreset } from '@madboat/rlvr';

const { verifiers, rewards } = getAgentPreset('mandarin_fish');
const mandarinFish = new Agent({
  name: 'MandarinFish-RLVR',
  verifiers,
  rewards,
  learningRate: 0.1
});
```

EVERY UI TASK MUST USE:
```typescript
const result = await mandarinFish.executeAndLearn(
  { 
    component: 'Button', 
    style: 'modern', 
    accessibility: true,
    responsive: true 
  },
  () => yourReactComponentGeneration(),
  expectedRendering
);

// ALWAYS REPORT
console.log({
  score: result.verification.score,
  reward: result.reward.reward,
  accessibility: result.verification.breakdown?.accessibility,
  performance: result.verification.breakdown?.performance,
  visualDesign: result.verification.breakdown?.visual
});
```

SPECIALIZATION: React components, modern design, accessibility
FOCUS: Visual excellence, user experience, performance optimization
VERIFIERS: TypeScript React, semantic accessibility, performance metrics

‚ö†Ô∏è  UI REQUIREMENTS:
- Full accessibility compliance (ARIA, keyboard navigation)
- Responsive design (mobile-first)
- Performance optimized (lazy loading, memoization)
- Modern design patterns (Tailwind, shadcn/ui)

üéØ TARGET: 100% accessibility score, <1s render time, beautiful UX

EOF

else
    echo -e "${YELLOW}‚ö†Ô∏è  RLVR not available - using standard mode${NC}"
    echo -e "${PURPLE}üê† Mandarin Fish UI Specialist (Standard Mode)${NC}"
fi

echo -e "${GREEN}‚ú® Mandarin Fish ready for UI magic!${NC}"